      <title>法国承认摩洛哥对西撒哈拉的统治 实现重大转变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/france-recognizes-moroccan-rule-of-western-sahara-in-major-shift</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国承认摩洛哥对西撒哈拉的主权，这一历史性转变可能会刺激对有争议的矿产资源丰富的地区的更多投资，但会进一步加剧与邻国阿尔及利亚的紧张关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/france-recognizes-moroccan-rule-of-western-sahara-in-major-shift</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 09:00:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
